```plantuml
@startuml unnmdnwb3_dora

actor User
participant "DORA API" as DoraAPI
participant "GitLab Connector" as GitLab
participant "Prometheus Connector" as Prometheus
participant "MongoDB Service" as MongoDB
participant "Metrics Calculation" as Metrics

User -> DoraAPI: Request DORA Metrics (GET /metrics)
activate DoraAPI

DoraAPI -> GitLab: Fetch GitLab Data (repos, PRs, pipelines)
activate GitLab
GitLab --> DoraAPI: Raw GitLab Data
deactivate GitLab

DoraAPI -> Prometheus: Query Alert Data
activate Prometheus
Prometheus --> DoraAPI: Alert Metrics
deactivate Prometheus

DoraAPI -> MongoDB: Retrieve Aggregated Data
activate MongoDB
MongoDB --> DoraAPI: Stored Metrics Data
deactivate MongoDB

DoraAPI -> Metrics: Calculate DORA Metrics
activate Metrics
Metrics --> DoraAPI: Calculated Metrics
deactivate Metrics

DoraAPI --> User: Return DORA Metrics
deactivate DoraAPI

@enduml
```